Detailed Description

Data structure for representing a single function .

jmi_func_t is a struct that contains function pointers and dimension information corresponding to a mathematical vector valued function, . The struct also contains function pointers to symbolic Jacobians and associated sparsity information and a pointer to a jmi_func_ad_t struct containing AD data (if compiled with AD support).
